</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
B1141: Prekinut strujni krug senzora temperature zraka u okolini (temperatura okoline)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Model s kontakt bravom:
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Napon kruga signala senzora temperature zraka u okolini neprestano je viši od 4,68 V u određenom vremenu.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Model sa sustavom pokretanja pritiskom prekidača, bez ključa:
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Napon kruga signala senzora temperature zraka u okolini neprestano je viši od 4,85 V u određenom vremenu.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Konektor / krug senzora temperature zraka u okolini
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Senzor temperature zraka u okolini
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
BCM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
B1142: Kratki spoj strujnog kruga senzora temperature zraka u okolini (temperatura okoline)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Model s kontakt bravom:
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Napon kruga signala senzora temperature zraka u okolini neprestano je niži od 0,14 V u određenom vremenu.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Model sa sustavom pokretanja pritiskom prekidača, bez ključa:
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Napon kruga signala senzora temperature zraka u okolini neprestano je niži od 0,15 V u određenom vremenu.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
